posting_body: ['1809 105th Street Court South, Tacoma, WA 98444', 'Heatherstone Apartments in Tacoma, WAHeatherstone Apartments is a beautiful community located just south of Tacoma, Washington.', 'Our community is located in a quiet neighborhood near schools, parks, and restaurants.', 'We are also conveniently close to I-5, Hwy 512, and Joint-Base Lewis McChord AFB.', 'We are a pet-friendly community and are located nearby nature trails for exercising your four-legged friends.', 'During the summer months, residents enjoy swimming in the heated outdoor pool and relaxing at the community cabana.', 'Our state-of-the-art fitness center, sport-court and outdoor playgrounds are great places for residents to enjoy and get their exercise.', 'Apartment Features:', 'Pet Friendly Home', 'High Speed Internet Access', 'Extra Storage', 'Disposal', 'Dishwasher', 'In-Unit Washer & Dryer', 'Community Features:', 'Zero Deposit Community', 'Community Cabana', 'Flexible Monthly Payments with Flex Rent', 'Fitness Center', 'Seasonal  Outdoor Pool', '24-Hour Maintenance', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
